{
  "title": "Savory Sweet Venezuelan Baby Plum Tomato Stew",
  "description": "This mustardy and chewy Venezuelan dish is a kid-friendly delight featuring baby plum tomatoes, perfect for a weeknight dinner. It is paleo-friendly and made with simple ingredients.",
